>- `apply_mode_to_commission` propagates `sampler_density` into `mode_sampler_density` metadata<br/>- tests verify each mode's value, propagation, and that `sampler_density` is bounded [0.0, 1.0] |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| 31 | T-031 | Register `voice_sampler` character in `character_registry.py` with `voice.synth = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sw_sampler\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"`, `voice.role = \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sampler\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"`, default register, and per-mode gain overrides. | T1 | 4 | 3 | CCS-008 | T-001 | - `character_registry.py` gains `voice_sampler` entry with synth=`sw_sampler`, role=`sampler`, register=`[36, 84]`, params containing default grain_size_ms, density, pitch_transpose<br/>- character is selectable by `select_cast_ids` when `preferred_synths` includes `sw_sampler`<br/>- tests verify registration and selection through cast planner |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| 32 | T-032 | Implement `sw_sampler.scd` granular SynthDef with bufnum, grain-size, density, position-scrub, pitch-transpose, attack/release envelope, and effects-bus send. | T1 | 4 | 3 | CCS-009 | T-001 | - SynthDef args: `bufnum`, `amp` (default 0.5), `grain_size_ms` (default 80, range 20–200), `density` (default 12 grains/sec), `position` (0..1 normalized), `position_rate` (scrub speed), `pitch_transpose_semitones` (default 0), `pitch_jitter_semitones` (default 0.1), `attack_sec` (default 0.05), `release_sec` (default 0.2), `gate` (default 1, sustained), `out_bus` (default 0), `fx_send` (default 0.4)<br/>- `doneAction:2` self-frees on envelope end<br/>- compiled `sw_sampler.scsyndef` lives in `synthesis/synthdefs/`<br/>- SC-side test (`my-claw/supercollider/test_sw_sampler.scd`) renders 2-second clip from a known buffer and verifies non-silence + spectral characteristics<br/>- gate=0 triggers release 