and, transient if high transient density, etc.). (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-009** [T1] Captured samples land in `samples/contact/` or `samples/room/` as 24-bit 48 kHz WAV with metadata-tagged filename and an entry in `index.sqlite`. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-010** [T1] Implement self-quotation loop: when a song completes with arc-payoff > threshold AND clicks=0, sample a 4-second window of `SuperCollider:out_1` for the next session. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n *Subtotal: ~30 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n@@ -32,47 +32,42 @@ Sprints are sequential. Tasks within a sprint can run in parallel unless a depen\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n **Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System), Sprint 1 (Quality Scoring)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-011** [T1] Implement R12 Sensor-to-Intent Aggregation Matrix: smoothed IIR + hysteresis → aggregate intentions (global_energy, global_restraint, global_brightness). (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-012** [T1] Implement bounded reactive delta track in scheduler with per-parameter modulation caps. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-013** [T1] Expose aggregate-intention telemetry (global_energy/restraint/brightness) in operator diagnostics, never raw one-to-one mappings. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-014** [T1] Build the metric battery: IOI CoV, velocity σ, DNVR/DNODR, pitch-class entropy H1, Grooving Similarity (GS), tempo autocorrelation ρ₁, LZ76 compression ratio, novelty peaks per phrase, silence-at-phrase-boundaries. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-015** [T1] Build anti-pattern tests: quantization ghosting, dynamic compression, motif ossification, random-as-expression (Ljung-Box), symmetric-arc uncanny, dead-silence failure. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-016** [T1] Implement performance-worm logger: 2D trajectory in tempo–loudness space + convex-hull area computation as CI artifact. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-017** [T1] Integrate metric battery + anti-pattern detectors into CI gate with fail-on-regression policy. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-018** [T1] Embed rule-stack provenance in exported audio metadata (e.g., WAV iXML chunk or sidecar JSON) for listener-review workflow. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-011** [T1] Implement anti-pattern detectors: `sampler_dominating` (sampler event count > 0.6 × total events) and `sampler_silent_quintet_member` (sampler used in <5% of last 50 pieces, mode-weighted). (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-012** [T1] End-to-end smoke test on cypherclaw: capture a known room sound, watch the composer self-quote it within 3 pieces, verify the self-listener observes the resulting peaks. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-013** [T2] Update `docs/cypherclaw-musicianship-roadmap.md` to reflect the quintet, document the sampler architecture in `docs/cypherclaw-sampler-architecture.md`, and add a one-page artistic-intent doc `docs/cypherclaw-sampler-artistic-intent.md`. (~6h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-*Subtotal: ~24 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+*Subtotal: ~12 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n ### Sprint 3: Improvement Engine Hardening\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n **Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System), Sprint 2 (Improvement Engine Hardening)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-019** [T1] Enforce role-filter gating across R1–R8 with a single shared contract; verify machine identity preservation end-to-end. (~3h) → deps: T-