sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:469:Per-feature human listening sessions, ordered so Feature 3 (streaming) verifies first. After CC-102 is approved, every other checkpoint publishes its reference sample as a labelled session in the cypherclaw.holdenu.com archive feed — Anthony reviews remotely via the public web page rather than from local files. Telegram notifications include the archive URL. The checkpoints are hard gates: features may be built in parallel but their listening sessions are sequenced behind streaming.
