sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:649:This is the human-in-the-loop checkpoint that engineering automation cannot replace.
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:664:- **Public endpoints:** all `/api/cypherclaw/*` endpoints that mutate state (POST /segment, POST /feature-update) require a shared-secret bearer token. Token rotated quarterly. cypherclaw-side has the secret in `/home/user/cypherclaw/.env` (chmod 600).
